title: Grand Theft Auto IV (GTA IV) REPACK
description:
The best release yet.

- Patch 1.0.7.0
- Reloaded Fix
- xliveless
- Native Trainer 6.5
- Supports Windows XP all up to Windows 10

Native Trainer controls:
Activate trainer menu - F3
Deactivate trainer menu - F4
Navigate up - Numpad 8
Navigate down - Numpad 2
Navigate left - Numpad 4
Navigate right - Numpad 6
Navigate back - Numpad 0
Select item - 5

Mount or burn to bluray & install. That's all! Simple as cake.
Hope you enjoy
